snippet.title: FIRST DAY OF AMBERRY SCHOOL | Bloxburg Highschool | Roblox
snippet.description:
Hi guys! Sorry I haven't uploaded in 2 weeks. I have been really sick and I'm still not 100% back to normal in this video but I really wanted to record. Today is the opening on Amberry High School. It will be the first time we let students in for their first full day of school. Today the kids will attend English, Math, Gym, Science and Baking. This is our first time being teachers so it doesnt go as smooth as we would have liked.

Thanks for watching! I have missed you guys :)

Play Bloxburg here:
https://www.roblox.com/games/185655149/Welcome-to-Bloxburg-BETA

"Build and design your own amazing house, own awesome vehicles, hang out with friends, work, roleplay or explore the city of Bloxburg. The possibilities are endless!"

If you want to watch the school tour click here:

I MADE A SCHOOL ON BLOXBURG | Berry High School | Bloxburg Tour:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QZr5ePhwwXU

Watch some of my other bloxburg videos:

AMBERRY HOTEL GRAND OPENING!!!| Our First Guests | Roblox Bloxburg
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=atvBOjwFUpg

I MADE A HOTEL ON BLOXBURG | Amberry Hotel | Bloxburg Tour | Roblox
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pW9cQ8LZC4Y


THE HOTEL MAIDS LAUNDRY ROOM on Amberry Hotel Update | Bloxburg Tour | Roblox:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8fMV5YU_s4k


AMBERRY COFFEE ☕ | Making a Coffee Shop on Bloxburg | Roblox
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G-zHTcbYu_w

I MADE MY REAL HOUSE ON BLOXBURG | Roblox Bloxburg London House Tour:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5A4ayd9tPYM

BUILDING MY DREAM HOUSE in ROBLOX | Bloxburg Tudor Cottage
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZnOphTN-uSk


What is roblox?
ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It’s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 8 to 18 year olds, Roblox is Kid friendly.PG, Family Friendly + No Swearing but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX — interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything.
